ETN

 entertainment services, namely, organizing, conducting, producing and exhibiting a championship street skateboarding event live and through the media Read More


Classification Information
Class [041]
Education and Entertainment Services

 Entertainment services, namely, organizing, conducting, producing and exhibiting a championship street skateboarding event live and through the media of television and the Internet


Class [035]
Advertising, Business & Retail Services

 Marketing services, namely, promoting the goods and services of others by arranging for sponsors to affiliate their goods and services with street skateboarding events; dissemination of advertising for others via an on-line electronic communications network; direct mail advertising for others; association services, namely, promoting the interests of professional street skateboarding; promoting for others events for professional street skateboarding; promoting public interest in professional street skateboarding; providing a live forum for professional street skateboarders to showcase, display, demonstrate and promote ideas, products, and services in connection with street skateboarding; providing marketing and promotion of special sporting and cultural events


Class [009]
Computer & Software Products & Electrical & Scientific Products

 Audio and video recordings featuring skateboards and skateboarding; downloadable digital media files featuring internet web links relating to skateboards and skateboarding; sunglasses


Class [016]
Paper Goods and Printed Material

 Printed matter, namely, posters for skateboarding and depicting images of skateboarding


Class [025]
Clothing Products

 Clothing for men, women, and children, namely, baseball caps, caps, shirts, sweaters, t-shirts


Class [038]
Communications Services

 Television broadcasting services in the field of skateboarding; television transmission services; cable television broadcasting; radio broadcasting; broadcasting programming on the Internet; information transmission via electronic communications networks; transmission of information through video communication systems; broadcasting services and provision of telecommunication access to video and audio content provided via a video on demand; streaming of audio material on the Internet; streaming of video material and podcasts on the Internet; electronic delivery of images and photos via a global computer network; providing multiple-user access to a global computer information network for the purpose of participating in interactive polling in the field of street skateboarding; wireless communications services, namely, transmission of text, graphics, data and entertainment information to mobile phones; mobile media and entertainment services in the nature of electronic transmission of entertainment media content
